join us.

Our employees play a crucial part in creating an outstanding school. Dipont Huayao Collegiate School’s unique structure and commitment to excellence, inside and outside of the classroom, represent a fantastic opportunity for ambitious and highly motivated individuals to further their careers.

 

We are building a diverse, enthusiastic and highly supportive community of staff who is committed to academic excellence and to creating opportunities for scholars to take charge of their learning.

 

Our staff should embody the same high standards and dispositions we expect our graduates to model. Every educator will be expected to contribute actively to the whole life of the school, working with scholars beyond the classroom in advisory, co-curricular and residential programs.

Opportunities at Huayao Collegiate

 

We always welcome applications from highly talented expatriate and Chinese staff who enjoy collaboration and learning, who embrace cross-cultural adaptability, and who share our resilient and ethical passion for developing an outstanding college preparatory school.

 

 

Find out more about our approach to learning and teaching.

Recruitment Process and Applications

 


As well as applying online via the links above, prospective staff can also email a CV and covering letter to careers@dipont-hc.com .

Our school is committed to safe recruitment practices and all our appointees will be subject to comprehensive reference and criminal records checks.

 

Professional Development

 

Our bilingual teacher training program for recent graduates or newly graduating students from education degrees will be available next year. Delivered by our highly experienced teacher training team, it incorporates theoretical learning in modern pedagogical approaches and practical learning through school placement.

Safe Recruitment Practices

 

 

Our school is committed to safe recruitment practices and all our appointees will be subject to comprehensive reference and criminal records checks.
